umnos<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Uno de los objetivos de la incorporaci\\u00f3n de ayudantes alumnos es la de propiciar un espacio para el inicio de un proceso de formaci\\u00f3n en la docencia universitaria en el marco de la gesti\\u00f3n de recursos humanos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para ser ayudante alumno ad-honorem se deben cumplir con los siguientes requisitos:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Ser alumno sistem\\u00e1tico de la UNPA - UARG.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Poseer aprobado el 20% de las materias correspondientes al Plan de Estudios.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Poseer aprobada la asignatura objeto del llamado a Inscripci\\u00f3n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Documentaci\\u00f3n a presentar:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Formulario de inscripci\\u00f3n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Fotocopia de DNI.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Curriculum Vitae.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Certificado de alumno regular, materias aprobadas, materias regularizadas y promedio.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2025-07-11 20:42:23\",\"created_by\":32,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2025-07-11 20:42:23\",\"modified_by\":32,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2025-07-11 20:42:23\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_catego